DTSTAMP:20260627T134753Z
DTSTART:20260809T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:HCP Members are invited to join our June Critique Group led by 
	Howard Bossen\, Professor Emeritus of Photography and Visual Communication
	\, School of Journalism at Michigan State University. You may register for
	 free as a Presenter and get feedback on your work from Castro and fellow 
	HCP members\, or as an Attendee and partake in the discussion. Our critiqu
	e groups provide a supportive and professional environment to share your w
	ork and take the next step. Please visit our Critique Groups page for \n\n
	https://www.edu.hcponline.org/events/summer26-critique-group-2\n\nFrom Hou
	ston Center for Photography
